i3d config tags =

-moddesc-
XMLData:modDescVersion:xxx                  modDesc version


-storeData-
XMLData:category:x                          category
XMLData:brand:x                             brand
XMLData:price:x                             price
XMLData:image:x                             image

-base-
XMLData:speedLimit                          speedLimit
XMLData:width                               width
XMLData:length                              length
XMLData:height                              height
XMLData:lengthoffset                        lengthoffset
XMLData:mapHotSpot                          mapHotSpot


-fillunit-
XMLData:vehicleType:xxx                     vehicleType, default to tractor when not foundation
XMLData:numberOfFillUnits:x                 number of fillUnits
XMLData:fillUnitX:Y                         fillunit<number>:<type>
XMLData:fillUnitCapacityX:Y                 fillunit<number>:<capacity>


-fillTrigger-
XMLData:fillTriggerFillUnitIndex:X          fillTrigger goes to unit <number>
XMLData:fillTriggerTriggerNode:X            fillTrigger trigger node
XMLData:fillTriggerLitersPerSecond:X        fillTrigger liters per second

-Drivable-
XMLData:steeringWheelIndoorRotation:X       steeringwheel indoor rotation
XMLData:steeringWheelOutdoorRotation:X      steeringwheel outdoor rotation

-Discharge-
XMLData:dischargeTrigger:X                  discharge trigger
XMLData:dischargeSound:X                    discharge sound

-LicensePlate-
XMLData:preferedLicenceFront:X              licenseplate type front
XMLData:preferedLicenceBack:X               licenseplate type rear

